data.description: Start your home journey in this home! As the electric bill skyrocket - NOT FOR THIS 3-bedroom 2 bath SOLAR PANEL HOME! Solar will be paid off at closing. Imagine the huge lifetime savings. Turn in key home with high vaulted ceilings, freshly painted rooms, with an indoor and outdoor patio, storage shed, 2 car garage, nicely done kitchen backsplash, master bedroom en suite with walk in closet, jet tubs and private lavatory/shower. Spacious dining area. Excellent home lay out. Roof is replaced 2013. Good condition, well maintained A/C and Water Heater unit. Make an offer soon!
